<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti</hi>
<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>
<lb n="3"/>maturai
<lb n="4"/>koṇṭa ko
<lb n="5"/>pparakecaripa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi>ṟ
<lb n="6"/>ku yāṇṭu 26
<lb n="7"/>Āvatu kuṉṟakkū
<lb n="8"/>ṟṟattu<hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>ya
<lb n="9"/>m ciṟupaḻuvūrt ti
<lb n="10"/>ruvālantuṟai<hi rend="grantha">maha</hi>
<lb n="11"/><hi rend="grantha">de</hi><unclear>va</unclear>rkku Iṭaiyāṟ
<lb n="12"/>ṟuppātti<unclear>cū</unclear>rai
<lb n="13"/>kkuṭaiyāṉ A<unclear>ṭi</unclear>kaṇi
<lb n="14"/>ḷavi vaitta non
<lb n="15"/>tāviḷakkoṉṟeriya
<lb n="16"/>vaitta cāvāmuvāppe
<lb n="17"/>{space} rāṭu 90 Itu
<lb n="18"/>{space} pa<hi rend="grantha">nmāhe</hi>
